灣算贏左架喇。"},{"pid":"f2ee2798094f2638722545cf782fd21780e144dd","tid":613292,"uid":33373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T12:45:29.000Z","msg":"on 9<br />\n行激進路線入咩議會"},{"pid":"33a2a793806dcffd40b6ab8cc75c00789510aefd","tid":613292,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T12:59:25.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不如你整個連登黨<br />\n所有投票會同連登仔討論<br />\n參考大家意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c74708ef59ca03b69bf7f818017c9dc57899aa5","tid":613292,"uid":174493,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T13:15:39.000Z","msg":"不如做個偽建制<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  真建一反就屌鳩佢話假和諧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打造一個以民為本既政黨用維尼熊思想做護盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 分薄建制狗票源<br />\n<br />\n造一份假撚過建制既民生政綱，行福利主義盡出安老政策呃鳩班廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0b803c1e8af55ddb2c606f7d4ccd3d49a8646b3","tid":613292,"uid":73897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c74708ef59ca03b69bf7f818017c9dc57899aa5","tid":613292,"uid":174493,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T13:15:39.000Z","msg":"不如做個偽建制<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  真建一反就屌鳩佢話假和諧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打造一個以民為本既政黨用維尼熊思想做護盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 分薄建制狗票源<br />\n<br />\n造一份假撚過建制既民生政綱，行福利主義盡出安老政策呃鳩班廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T13:50:11.000Z","msg":"玩膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一陣好似中間超人噉"},{"pid":"7b07e16c7ed06e23be504c83eb3497b33d338c72","tid":613292,"uid":174493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0b803c1e8af55ddb2c606f7d4ccd3d49